      "description": "Mỗi TC = 4 requests:\nR1: POST /research/stream (lấy thread_id + Interrupt 1)\nR2: POST /research/resume (Interrupt 2: outline)\nR3: POST /research/resume (Interrupt 3: routing)\nR4: POST /research/resume → {type:done}",
